title: Hour 1: NFL Whip Around
description:
Stephen A, Chris "Mad Dog" Russo and Jeff Saturday dive into NFL Week 1 topics: Who will win the NFC East, would you bank on the Bucs to go to win the Super Bowl and who will be benched first: Lance or Trubisky?
